room_title: Escape room "Hexed" by Enigma Escape Experience in Salem
room_description: Does an ancient culture guard a secret connection to our solar system? Your archaeologist friend seems to think so. His recent letters tell of his many desperate attempts to uncover the forbidden secrets of a lost people and their unique artifacts. Will he succeed or will he delve too greedily and too deeply into the forbidden? A tattered package has just arrived which may contain answers.
